Paper: hep-th/9512021

Date: 1995-12-05

Title: A Suggestion for Modification of Vafa-Witten Theory

Comments: Latex, 23kb, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B378 (1996) 147-152

Using the Mathai-Quillen formalism we reexamine the twisted N=4supersymmetric model of Vafa-Witten theory. Smooth out the relation between thesupersymmetric action and the path integral representation of the Thom class.